### Service Root

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog

### Metadata

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/$metadata

### Get All Books

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books

### Get Single Book

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)

### Get with Filter

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=price gt 200

### Get with OrderBy

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$orderby=price desc

### Get Top Records

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$top=2

### Get Skip Records

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$skip=1

### Count

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books/$count

### Create Book (POST)

POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "CAP Guide",
"Author": "Abhishek",
"price": 450,
"publishDate": "2024-05-01T10:00:00",
"digitalCopy": true
}

### Create Book 2

POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "NodeJS Basics",
"Author": "Rohit",
"price": 299,
"publishDate": "2023-12-10T09:30:00",
"digitalCopy": false
}

### Update Book (PATCH)

PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)
Content-Type: application/json

{
"price": 999
}

### Update Multiple Fields

PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "Updated Book",
"price": 555
}

### Delete Book

DELETE http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111)

### Delete Another Book

DELETE http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books(22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222)

### Search (contains)

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=contains(title,'CAP')

### Filter Boolean

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=digitalCopy eq true

### Filter Price Range

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$filter=price gt 100 and price lt 500

### Select Fields

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$select=title,price

### Expand (for future association)

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Books?$expand=*

### Assosiation 

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/relationship/Header

###

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/relationship/Items
